<TEXT>
Johannesburg ended lower in thin trading, the overall index losing 25 to
4,610. Golds fell 38 or 1.8 per cent to 2,088 and industrials picked up from
the day's lows to finish 12 easier at 5,164. De Beers shed R3 to R103.
