3 per cent to Pounds 7.65m in the year to September 30.
Turnover increased by 11 per cent to Pounds 27.1m.
Earnings per share rose to 8.9p (8.5p) and a recommended final dividend of
3.95p, gives an 8 per cent rise to 5.5p (5.1p).
