insurance and Pounds 996,000 (Pounds 3.74m) on reinsurance.
Investment and other income was lower at Pounds 2.79m (Pounds 3.34m).
Administrative expenses amounted to Pounds 22.3m (Pounds 20.3m).
Profits included Pounds 27,000 in income from associated undertakings,
compared with Pounds 5,000 last year.
